Package org.wattdepot.server.restlet

Provides classes for the Restlet ServerResources.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AdminServerResource
    AdministratorServerResource - Administrative interface for WattDepot.
    CollectorMetaDataServerResource
    CollectorMetaDataServerResource - Handles the CollectorMetaData HTTP API (("/wattdepot/{group_id}/sensorprocess/", "/wattdepot/{group_id}/sensorprocess/{sensorprocess_id}").
    CollectorMetaDatasServerResource
    SensorProcessesServerResource - Handles the SensorProcesses HTTP API ("/wattdepot/{group_id}/sensorprocesses/").
    DepositoriesServerResource
    DepositorysServerResource - ServerResource that handles Depositories.
    DepositoryMeasurementServerResource
    DepositoryMeasurementServerResource - Handles the Measurement HTTP API ("/wattdepot/{group_id}/depository/{depository_id}/measurement/").
    DepositoryMeasurementsServerResource
    DepositoryMeasurementsServerResource - Handles the Depository measurements HTTP API ("/wattdepot/{group_id}/depository/{depository_id}/measurements/").
    DepositorySensorsServerResource
    DepositorySensorsServerResource - Handles the Depository sensors HTTP API ("/wattdepot/{group_id}/depository/{depository_id}/sensors/").
    DepositoryServerResource
    DepositoryServerResource - Handles Depository HTTP API ("/wattdepot/{group_id}/depository/", "/wattdepot/{group_id}/depository/{depository_id}").
    DepositoryValueServerResource
    DepositoryValueServerResource - ServerResouce that handles the GET /wattdepot/{group_id}/depository/{depository_id}/value/ response.
    JScience
    JScience - Testing the JScience classes.
    LoginPageServerResource
    AdministratorServerResource - Administrative interface for WattDepot.
    LoginServerResource
    LoginServerResource - Handles the login form.
    MeasurementTypeServerResource
    MeasurementTypeServerResource - Handles the MeasurementType HTTP API ("/wattdepot/measurementtype/" and "/wattdepot/measurementtype/{measurementtype_id}").
    MeasurementTypesServerResource
    MeasurementTypesServerResource - ServerResource that handles the URI "/wattdepot/measurementtypes/".
    SensorGroupServerResource
    SensorGroupServerResource - Handles the SensorGroup HTTP API ("/wattdepot/{group_id}/sensorgroup/", "/wattdepot/{group_id}/sensorgroup/{sensorgroup_id}").
    SensorGroupsServerResource
    SensorGroupsServerResource - Handles the SensorGroups HTTP API ("/wattdepot/{group_id}/sensorgroups/").
    SensorLocationServerResource
    LocationResource - WattDepot 3 Location Resource handles the Location HTTP API ("/wattdepot/{group_id}/location/" and "/wattdepot/{group_id}/location/{location_id}").
    SensorLocationsServerResource
    LocationsServerResource - ServerResource that handles the URI "/wattdepot/{group_id}/locations/".
    SensorModelServerResource
    SensorModelServerResource - Handles the SensorModel HTTP API ("/wattdepot/sensormodel/", "/wattdepot/sensormodel/{sensormodel_id}").
    SensorModelsServerResource
    SensorModelsServerResource - Handles the SensorGroups HTTP API ("/wattdepot/{group_id}/sensormodels/").
    SensorServerResource
    SensorServerResource - Handles the Sensor HTTP API ("/wattdepot/{group_id}/sensor/", "/wattdepot/{group_id}/sensor/{sensor_id}").
    SensorsServerResource
    SensorsServerResource - Handles the Sensors HTTP API ("/wattdepot/{group_id}/sensors/").
    UserGroupServerResource
    UserGroupServerResource - Handles the HTTP API ("/wattdepot/{group_id}/usergroup/", "/wattdepot/{group_id}/usergroup/{usergroup_id}").
    UserGroupsServerResource
    UserGroupsServerResource - Handles the UserGroup HTTP API ("/wattdepot/{group_id}/groups").
    UserInfoServerResource
    UserInfoServerResource - Handles the UserInfo HTTP API ("/wattdepot/{group_id}/user/{user_id}").
    UserPasswordServerResource
    UserPasswordServerResource - Handles the UserPassword HTTP API ("/wattdepot/{group_id}/userpassword/{user_id}").
    WattDepotServerResource
    WattDepotServerResource - Base class for WattDepot ServerResources.
